title: Jaime Winstone shows off her baby bump in sheer top at Dynamo's latest show
text:
Jaime Winstone shows off her baby bump in sheer top at Dynamo's latest show Jaime Winstone shows off her baby bump in sheer top at Dynamo's latest show 
Press Association 2014 / / National Entertainment News Share 
Jaime Winstone revealed her growing bump in a sheer black top as she walked down the red carpet at the Hammersmith Apollo on Thursday. 
The 30-year-old pregnant actress looked happy as she headed inside to watch magician Dynamo perform for the crowds. (David Fisher/REX) 
Wearing her hair tied up in braids, she flashed her bra and burgeoning stomach in the see-through top and wrapped up in a leather jacket. 
Jaime matched her polished red lips to her top, which had a similar stitched design on it. 
The daughter of film legend Ray Winstone announced she and DJ boyfriend James Suckling were having a child in early September through an Instagram snap. 
Standing with friend Miquita Oliver cradling her stomach, Jaime captioned the pic, “Me and @james_suckling are very pleased that we are having a baby!! 
“So Magic, I’m going to be a mama here is auntie @miquitaoliver having a cuddle xxx” 
Despite documenting her pregnancy on Instagram, Jaime has been covering up her tummy while out and about recently but she looked incredibly proud of her mother-to-be status on the red carpet. Share article 
This will be Jaime’s first child, although her boyfriend has two sons from a previous relationship. Promoted Stories
